Abstract

5314 individual reviewers contributed to the peer review process at Communications Biology in 2020. We acknowledge and thank each of them here.

Communications Biology received more than 3000 research and review article submissions last year, of which over 1700 were sent for external review. In all, 5314 individuals gave their time to ensure a fair and thorough peer review process in the uniquely challenging year that was 2020. These individuals are recognized below in alphabetical order by surname. We are truly grateful to all of our reviewers. Journal staff take full responsibility for any misspellings, omissions, or other errors.
